features: INSPIRED BY POPULAR SHORT VIDEOS: Deriving inspiration from trending short videos, we've animated the Skibidi Toilet Titan Clockman. Meticulously chosen for its popularity, Titan Clockman has been brought to life and infused with energy through action figures. In these figures, you'll witness a faithful reproduction of all the character designs, featuring the colossal golden alarm clock as the head, the entire body clad in golden armor, light cannons, and the golden core adorned with clocks and gears.

AS THE PERFECT CREATIVE GIFT, the Skibidi Toilet Multiverse Series Titan Clockman action figures make an ideal choice for boys and girls. It's a fantastic gift option for occasions like birthdays, Christmas, and Halloween. The most beloved and super-powered character is sure to make kids scream with excitement.

FEATURING A CLEVER JOINT MOBILITY DESIGN, the Titan Clockman's arms and head seamlessly articulate, simulating human joints with adjustable rotation angles. You can pose them in any way you desire, enhancing interactivity and fun. It stands at a height of 6.1 inches and a width of 3.15 inches.
HIGH-QUALITY MATERIALS, All skibidi toilet series action figures are made from top-grade ABS materials, non-toxic, odorless, and smooth, ensuring the safety of children.

OUTSTANDING PARTY DECORATION, the Skibidi Toilet Titan Clockman action figure delivers more than just fun. It can also serve as a charming decor for bedrooms, desks, and offices, making it the perfect decoration for party supplies.
